Caching in Restful Services
---------------------------
communication-stateless
-----------------------
one of the key principle of restful services in achieving scalability is "communication-stateless", which means the server should not store the data onbehalf the client. The client by himself should store the data locally at the client-side and use it whenever it is necessary.
	
	
